	
			     GtkMathView
	     A GTK Widget for Rendering MathML Documents

Full documentation is available on-line at

	http://www.cs.unibo.it/helm/mml-widget/

In the same page you can also find instruction to subscribe to the
GtkMathView mailing list. For subscriptions, send an e-mail with
empty subject and empty body to the following address:

	gtkmathview-subscribe@cs.unibo.it

This code is released under the GPL (see COPYING for more details).

See the file INSTALL for information about compiling, installing and
linking the package.

Starting from version 0.2.0 two programs are included with the
distribution. `mathmlviewer' is a simple viewer for MathML documents,
`mathml2ps' is a first attempt to convert a MathML formula to PostScript.

Luca Padovani <luca.padovani@cs.unibo.it>
